name: BigQueryDestination
description:
The BigQuery location for the output content.

params.name: data.output_uri
params.description: Required. BigQuery URI to a project or table, up to 2000 characters long. When only the project is specified, the Dataset and Table is created. When the full table reference is specified, the Dataset must exist and table must not exist. Accepted forms: * BigQuery path.
